From: SJ Park <sj@kernel.org>
Date: Fri, 3 Jul 2026 15:36:57 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] mm/damon/core: fixup has_probe_weights setup

Signed-off-by: SJ Park <sj@kernel.org>
---
 mm/damon/core.c | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/mm/damon/core.c b/mm/damon/core.c
index 9f516964a2e6d..439fafb00443b 100644
--- a/mm/damon/core.c
+++ b/mm/damon/core.c
@@ -1719,6 +1719,7 @@ static int __damon_commit_ctx(struct damon_ctx *dst, struct damon_ctx *src)
 	dst->addr_unit = src->addr_unit;
 	dst->min_region_sz = src->min_region_sz;
 
+	dst->has_probe_weights = false;
 	damon_for_each_probe(probe, dst) {
 		if (probe->weight)
 			dst->has_probe_weights = true;
-- 
2.47.3

